Like many of <COREF ID="97" TYPE="IDENT">his</COREF> contemporary surrealists , <COREF ID="97" TYPE="IDENT">Bunuel</COREF> is a paradox who on one hand claims apathy towards ultimate end , being , and Being , yet on the other hand loads <COREF ID="97" TYPE="IDENT">his</COREF> impressive body of work with moribund imagery and strange ideas about the God <COREF ID="97" TYPE="IDENT">he</COREF> so vociferously denies .
