<COREF ID="97" TYPE="IDENT">His</COREF> aims were specific : through the surreal , visualizing the impulses of the uncon - scious , <COREF ID="97" TYPE="IDENT">he</COREF> would , <COREF ID="97" TYPE="IDENT">he</COREF> said , `` shatter the optimism of the bourgeoisie world and force the reader -LRB- or spectator -RRB- to question the permanency of the prevailing order '' -LRB- Mellen 3 -RRB- .
