<COREF ID="107" TYPE="IDENT">He</COREF> went on to say , `` The purpose of surrealism was not to create a new literary , artistic , or even philosophical movement , but to explode the social order , to transform <COREF ID="79" TYPE="IDENT">life <COREF ID="79" TYPE="IDENT">itself</COREF></COREF> ' -LRB- 107 -RRB- .
