<COREF ID="84" TYPE="IDENT">a man</COREF> wipes <COREF ID="84" TYPE="IDENT">his</COREF> mouth completely off <COREF ID="84" TYPE="IDENT">his</COREF> face ,
dead donkey carcasses adorn a piano ,
