For the first time in <COREF ID="107" TYPE="IDENT">my</COREF> life , <COREF ID="107" TYPE="IDENT">I</COREF> 'd come into contact with <COREF ID="66" TYPE="IDENT">a coherent moral system that , as far as <COREF ID="107" TYPE="IDENT">I</COREF> could tell , had no flaws</COREF> .
